<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN">
<html><head><meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="content-type"><title></title></head><body class="c14 doc-content" style="background-color: #ffffff; max-width: 451.4pt; padding: 72pt 72pt 72pt 72pt;">
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Hi redacted,</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Did you know your body already has everything it needs to repair nerve damage?</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">It's true.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Every single night, while you sredactedp, your body naturally activates a process called "neural renewal."</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">It's an incredible system that repairs damaged nerve cells, restores myelin sheaths, and eliminates pain signals.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">The problem isn't that your nerves are permanently damaged.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">The problem is that something is blocking this natural healing process from working.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Let me explain...</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Johns Hopkins researchers recently discovered something that changes everything we thought we knew about neuropathy.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">They found that a specific protein buildup around nerve endings physically prevents your neural renewal from functioning properly.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Think of it like trying to breathe through a mask filled with mud.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">No matter how strong your lungs are, you simply can't get enough air.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">This discovery explains why:</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">&#128073; Your pain is often worse in the morning (neural renewal was blocked all night)</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">&#128073;Medications only provide temporary relief (they don't remove the blockage)</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">&#128073;Your symptoms get progressively worse (more blockage accumulates over time)</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">&#128073;Standard treatments eventually stop working (the blockage becomes too dense)</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">But here's the exciting part...</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">When this protein blockage is dissolved, your body's natural neural renewal process immediately kicks back into action.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">No need to "heal" your nerves with external treatments.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">No need for more powerful medications.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">No need for invasive procedures.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">Your body already knows exactly what to do - it just needs the blockage removed.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">And that's where this strange bedtime ritual comes in...</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">It involves something unexpected: pepper seeds.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">I can't reveal exactly how it works here (you need to see the presentation for that)...</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
    <p class="c1" style="line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;">
      <span class="c3" style="color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;">But what I can tell you is that something in these ordinary seeds triggers a reaction that dissolves the blockage overnight.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="c0" style="height: 11pt; line-height: 1.15; orphans: 2; padding-bottom: 0pt; padding-top: 0pt; text-align: left; widows: 2; color: #000000; font-family: 'Arial'; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0;"></p>
